AT.name: Kung Fu FIGHT!
AT.description: Fight the bad guys, save the girl - you know the drill! Relentless old-school action as you run, jump and fight your way through your quest of rescue and revenge. • Non-stop action! • Retro-styled, old school gameplay. • Battle through varied environments against unique enemies. • Multiple difficulty modes add challenge and replayability.
